---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title='Contacto'>
  <section
    class='w-full pt-2 md:h-[100dvh] h-[1583px] text-white flex flex-col justify-center items-center'
  >
    <div class='w-[700px] md:w-[537px] h-auto'>
      <h1 class='text-2xl md:text-[22px] font-medium'>Conecta con nosotros</h1>
      <p class='text-xl md:text-[15px] my-2 text-[var(--fourth-gray-color)]'>
        Bienvenido a Creemos Capital, rellena el siguiente formulario que tienes
        a continuacion y contacta con nosotros, estaremos encantados de escuchar
        tus dudas y comentarios.
      </p>
      <form
        class='w-full my-10 text-xl md:text-[15px] flex flex-col justify-center items-center'
      >
        <section class='w-full flex gap-5'>
          <div>
            <label for='name'>Nombres <span class='important'>*</span></label>
            <input
              type='text'
              id='name'
              name='name'
              required
              autocomplete='off'
              class='form-input w-[340px] md:w-[260px] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[var(--secondary-color)] transisition-all duration-200 ease-in'
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for='last_name'>
              Apellidos <span class='important'>*</span>
            </label>
            <input
              type='text'
              id='last_name'
              name='last_name'
              required
              autocomplete='off'
              class='form-input w-[340px] md:w-[260px] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[var(--secondary-color)] transisition-all duration-200 ease-in'
            />
          </div>
        </section>
        <div class='w-full'>
          <label for='email'>
            Correo Electr√≥nico <span class='important'>*</span>
          </label>
          <input
            type='email'
            id='email'
            name='email'
            required
            autocomplete='off'
            class='form-input w-full focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[var(--secondary-color)] transisition-all duration-200 ease-in'
          />
        </div>
        <div class='w-full'>
          <label for='message'>Mensaje <span class='important'>*</span></label>
          <textarea
            id='message'
            name='message'
            required
            class='w-full h-[150px] text-black bg-white rounded-[10px] resize-none my-[15px] p-2 md:p-[10px] whitespace-nowrap overflow-hidden focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[var(--secondary-color)] transisition-all duration-200 ease-in'
          >
          </textarea>
        </div>
        <button type='submit' class='submit-button'>Enviar</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .form-input {
    height: 37px;
    background-color: white;
    padding: 0px 10px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin: 15px 0px;
    color: black;
  }

  .important {
    color: red;
    margin: 0px 5px;
  }

  .submit-button {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    padding: 10px;
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: white;
    transition: all 0.4s ease-in-out;
  }

  .submit-button:hover {
    background: white;
    color: black;
  }
</style>
